title: BRIEF-Immunocellular Therapeutics Announces Achievement Of Next Key Milestone In Stem-To-T-Cell Research Immuno Oncology Program
text:
April 12, 2018 / 10:10 AM / in 8 minutes BRIEF-Immunocellular Therapeutics Announces Achievement Of Next Key Milestone In Stem-To-T-Cell Research Immuno Oncology Program Reuters Staff 
April 12 (Reuters) - ImmunoCellular Therapeutics Ltd : 
* IMMUNOCELLULAR THERAPEUTICS ANNOUNCES ACHIEVEMENT OF NEXT KEY MILESTONE IN STEM-TO-T-CELL RESEARCH IMMUNO-ONCOLOGY PROGRAM 
* BEEN ABLE TO VERIFY SUCCESSFUL TRANSFER OF SELECTED T CELL RECEPTOR GENETIC MATERIAL INTO HUMAN HEMATOPOIETIC STEM CELLS Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
